{"tid":118992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱心疼女兒嘔至滿身穢物 父脫其衣舐勻全身今認非禮","createTime":"2017-02-13T12:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T17:12:14.000Z","uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e849f0286e6bc323107236748da54b81d6c554da","tid":118992,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/200135_6d3ff62519418dbed6b11ad4f279dc56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F200135_6d3ff62519418dbed6b11ad4f279dc56.jpg&h=fd9a1cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年62歲的父親於約7年前見當時12歲的女兒不適嘔吐，稱見到對方嘔至滿身穢物而感心疼，於是脫光女兒的衣服舐其全身，女兒當時無力反抗，一直啞忍多年，期間父親又試過趁其睡覺時掀起其裙。至前年事主在網上透露持續遭父親侵犯，並向認識的社工稱有意尋死，社工終報警。<br />\n<br />\n無業並領綜援的父親原被控4項非禮罪，今在區院承認其中兩項罪名，其餘兩罪留於法庭存檔。法官對於被告稱因心疼女兒而犯案的說法直指難以接受，又指被告趁女兒不適而侵犯，行為令人反感，而且當時女兒沒有反抗能力，遂將被告還柙至3月13日判刑，期間取得事主的創傷報告。<br />\n<br />\n據控方案情指，被告與妻子共育有3子女，現年19歲的事主一直與被告關係欠佳，兩人甚少說話。首次案發時事主因不適而從學校早退，返家後被告給藥事主服用，事主感到頭暈及嘔吐，迷糊間感到被告替她脫衣並對她的身體又吻又舐，事主因不適而最終睡著。至事主15歲某日，事主於胞妹房間睡覺，迷糊間感到有人掀起其裙，她睜開眼發現被告手執其裙，於是喝退被告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今求情透露妻子在得悉事件後已跟他離婚，又強調當日給女兒服用的是退燒藥而非迷暈藥，犯案全因心疼女兒吐至全身是穢物，而他在犯案兩至三分鐘後已停止，現感到後悔，亦自知「過咗火位」，又指另一項非禮罪只是想替女兒整理衣服。"},{"pid":"bba971cb134fe8f55ea57c42a0a9fee5b245023b","tid":118992,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f48ebda19e15cafe31ec0fdbf558f5df7fa180f","tid":118992,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"衣家啲幾十後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6212b083484f49c47a201df8e67c86cc9cbc4f93","tid":118992,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:21:22.000Z","msg":"禁斷介護<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630c89d5322c3e0348c3e3629712658e15f215d4","tid":118992,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"又係廢老"},{"pid":"ee6aa4297f6ac1d1a50e979dfaee08eb32870948","tid":118992,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啦"},{"pid":"3415f0008f04a5cd4ea371489959100bdf1958f8","tid":118992,"uid":3734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:55:51.000Z","msg":"蘋果一日報兩單廢老風化案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a4996834e11aadcd76c77e679affd7aa339c37","tid":118992,"uid":51343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a580f58a23d4212958d21af2bf083f1c41e5d8","tid":118992,"uid":4484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"825c732e446627ecbb3ea6c7a30f9aae491897a1","tid":118992,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a208824f8639fe35b7b49caca9aaa7d8fb0752cb","tid":118992,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:31:40.000Z","msg":"幼幼"},{"pid":"b4b2a50f83eec7b108f304990c4ab949738b6c52","tid":118992,"uid":4200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"戀童"},{"pid":"0407ce75dc3d11df1b63b264b9c6ed623dd67a0f","tid":118992,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf64532ce5bd57111454e4f40400139cdcd0e938","tid":118992,"uid":117458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03571e73a380ab0f28ee30d58a4905d7dbaa4157","tid":118992,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:12:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">性罪行監躉</span></span>"}]}